---
title: Striploin Steaks and Herb Butter with Creamy Sweet Potato Mash and Maple-Dijon Bacon Broccolini
description: These striploin steaks are smothered in herb butter for a sumptuous flavour boost, but there's so much more to tonight's meal. The mash is super creamy, and the broccolini is taken to a new level with bacon and a maple-Dijon sauce.
